reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality for price
reviews.reviewText: Cute little car!For the price you get what you pay for. These are no “hot wheels” cars and they are plastic so be careful! They are good for the price though and it comes with so many! It’s got a handle for kids to carry and looks adorable!This keeps kids entertained for days on end and the only thing that would make this better would be a car play mat! But all in all you get more what you pay for and I’m sure any kid would appreciate a toy like this! The small construction toys have pieces on them that move so they’re not just boring construction cars, they’re entertaining.
